rows.label: qst650312_msg0001
rows.name:
Now you look like a guy who needs
a serious slice of assistance!

rows.label: qst650312_msg0003
rows.name:
Eyup, Kurtos-san!
I haven't seen you in ages!

rows.label: qst650312_msg0004
rows.name: Rex, m'lad! How goes?

rows.label: qst650312_msg0005
rows.name:
Say, by the by... The monsters
around here have been getting to be
a right pain lately.

rows.label: qst650312_msg0006
rows.name:
I'm worried they might find their
way up to the village guardian, or start
hassling the other islands...

rows.label: qst650312_msg0007
rows.name: Yeah, we don't want that happening...

rows.label: qst650312_msg0008
rows.name: Looks like our time to shine, eh, Rex?

rows.label: qst650312_msg0009
rows.name: I suppose so, yeah!

rows.label: qst650312_msg0010
rows.name: How can we help you, Kurtos-san?

rows.label: qst650312_msg0011
rows.name: Oh, you're a good lad, so you are!

rows.label: qst650312_msg0012
rows.name:
Well, there's a colony of Flow Bunnits
down by Rigitte Harbor or wherever
you can find 'em that need regulating.

rows.label: qst650312_msg0013
rows.name:
Sloam Runners'll need to be taught
a lesson too. Around Daram Isle and
the like.

rows.label: qst650312_msg0014
rows.name:
Those Segel Ansel have been nothing
but trouble, neither. Could you give
them a whupping?

rows.label: qst650312_msg0015
rows.name:
Aye, the Buma Hiln an' all. The ones
around Iyasaki.

rows.label: qst650312_msg0016
rows.name:
If you could take out a few Yurem
Puffot or so while you're at it, I'd
be ever so grateful...

rows.label: qst650312_msg0017
rows.name: Gotcha. Anything else?

rows.label: qst650312_msg0018
rows.name: No, I think that's pretty mu-

rows.label: qst650312_msg0019
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Oi! Hold up!

rows.label: qst650312_msg0020
rows.name:
What about those Stream Navy that
need gathering? They aren't gonna
fish themselves up!

rows.label: qst650312_msg0021
rows.name:
Can you get us some Killi-Killi Killifish
as well?

rows.label: qst650312_msg0022
rows.name: Crikey...

rows.label: qst650312_msg0023
rows.name:
I know, it's a lot. But is there anyone
else around here who's up to the task?
I think not.

rows.label: qst650312_msg0024
rows.name:
Can't argue with you there.
All right, let's get down to business!
